=head1 DESCRIPTION

An optional configuration within the C<SchedulingConfig> to setup a
recurring maintenance window with a predetermined start time and
duration for the rollout of a job document to all devices in a target
group for a job.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> DurationInMinutes => Int

Displays the duration of the next maintenance window.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> StartTime => Str

Displays the start time of the next maintenance window.



